\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fancy_Crane\", \"score\": 0.999999998662588, \"rank\": 1.3372150988155234e-09, \"text\": \"Fancy\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fancy_Crane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fancy_Crane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pablo Gutierrez\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 220}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 262, \"to\": 269}, {\"ngram\": \"surfboards\", \"from\": 282, \"to\": 292}, {\"ngram\": \"parachute-like sails\", \"from\": 294, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"slender hydrofoils\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 370, \"to\": 379}, {\"ngram\": \"80 kilometers\", \"from\": 385, \"to\": 398}, {\"ngram\": \"hour\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many do, which is why \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cFormula Kite racing \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 the fastest sport at the Summer Games \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 has generated considerable excitement and anticipation ahead of its Olympic debut.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cFormula Kite\", \"from\": 433, \"to\": 448}, {\"ngram\": \"the fastest sport\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 477}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Games\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"considerable excitement\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"anticipation\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 556}, {\"ngram\": \"its Olympic debut\", \"from\": 566, \"to\": 583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While it's a novelty for some, for Slovenian Formula Kite racer Toni Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek it's an everyday quest.\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 687, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"score\": 0.97255597101768, \"rank\": 0.028079722318575383, \"text\": \"Slovenian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Slovenia\"}, {\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kite\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.192757270855735e-35, \"text\": \"Kite\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kite\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kite\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a novelty\", \"from\": 597, \"to\": 606}, {\"ngram\": \"an everyday quest\", \"from\": 669, \"to\": 686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Under clear blue skies on the vast Mediterranean, Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek catches the morning wind.\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"clear blue skies\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the vast Mediterranean\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 736}, {\"ngram\": \"Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning wind\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 771}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As each gust propels him forward, his sleek board slices through the water \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 and as he fine-tunes his skills for the upcoming Olympics, he knows precision and agility will be crucial.\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 958, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each gust\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 785}, {\"ngram\": \"his sleek board slices\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 847}, {\"ngram\": \"his skills\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming Olympics\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 909}, {\"ngram\": \"precision\", \"from\": 920, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"agility\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 941}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cIn his hometown of Koper, where his passion for kiteboarding began, Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek took a break from the water to explore the coastal streets on bicycles with CGTN correspondent Pablo Gutierrez.\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 982, \"end\": 987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koper\", \"score\": 0.9995931220524518, \"rank\": 0.0004070435644917277, \"text\": \"Koper\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Koper\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his hometown\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"his passion\", \"from\": 995, \"to\": 1006}, {\"ngram\": \"kiteboarding\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1052}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1067}, {\"ngram\": \"the coastal streets\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1098}, {\"ngram\": \"bicycles\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"CGTN correspondent Pablo Gutierrez\", \"from\": 1116, \"to\": 1150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as he geared up for sport's most significant event, the local community was eager to support their hometown hero.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1269, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport's most significant event\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"the local community\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"their hometown hero\", \"from\": 1249, \"to\": 1268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008c\\\"I know that my sport is not yet massive \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 it is growing,\\\" Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek remarked.\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1353, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my sport\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek\", \"from\": 1335, \"to\": 1343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just hope to be a good inspiration for the new generation coming up.\\\"\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good inspiration\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1391}, {\"ngram\": \"the new generation\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cVodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek is one of 40 competitors\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009420 men and 20 women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094vying for gold at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cVodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"40 competitors\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009420 men\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1473}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1499, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1519}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes will race up to four times daily, aiming for a target time of around 11 minutes on courses approximately 10 kilometers long situated at the Marseille Marina \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 further along the sparkling Mediterranean.\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1683, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"score\": 0.997257736885898, \"rank\": 0.002749803799647276, \"text\": \"Marseille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marseille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1533}, {\"ngram\": \"a target time\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"around 11 minutes\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1613}, {\"ngram\": \"courses\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"the sparkling Mediterranean\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1736}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cIs it exciting to be part of a sport breaking through into international prominence, on the biggest stage of all?\", \"from\": 1739, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1767}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"international prominence\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest stage\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1847}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Definitely, it is,\\\" smiled Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek.\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1894, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Whenever I think about it, my heart is pounding, and for the sport to become Olympic, that steps it to the next level.\\\"\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my heart\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"the next level\", \"from\": 1999, \"to\": 2013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE Denmark's Mandarin-speaking badminton champ Refugee team seeks first Olympic medal Hungarian judo star fights for his sport \\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cFormula Kite racing requires exceptional skill, with athletes navigating hydrofoil boards at high speeds.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2028, \"end\": 2035, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9999795549400017, \"rank\": 1.989652784669156e-05, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}, {\"begin\": 2073, \"end\": 2080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee\", \"score\": 0.9999999999540705, \"rank\": 4.5733405861859275e-11, \"text\": \"Refugee\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Refugee\"}, {\"begin\": 2113, \"end\": 2122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.7291252116861041, \"rank\": 0.37149668138288755, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"first Olympic medal\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"his sport\", \"from\": 2141, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cFormula Kite racing\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"exceptional skill\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2200}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2207, \"to\": 2215}, {\"ngram\": \"hydrofoil boards\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2243}, {\"ngram\": \"high speeds\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2258}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They wear helmets, goggles, and impact vests for safety as they maneuver through challenging courses, avoiding obstacles while maintaining top speeds.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2414, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"helmets\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"goggles\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"impact vests\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"safety\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"challenging courses\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2364}, {\"ngram\": \"obstacles\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"top speeds\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2413}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cVodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek's journey in kiteboarding began at a young age, under the guidance of his father, Rajko Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek, an accomplished windsurfer who proudly recounted the boy's history of confidently following in his father's footsteps.\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2644, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2522, \"end\": 2524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelvin\", \"score\": 0.9995809005317807, \"rank\": 0.00041891966083133363, \"text\": \"ek\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelvin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelvin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cVodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek's journey\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2437}, {\"ngram\": \"kiteboarding\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"a young age\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"the guidance\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2508}, {\"ngram\": \"an accomplished windsurfer\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"the boy's history\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"his father's footsteps\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At two years, he was skiing,\\\" Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek senior told CGTN.\", \"from\": 2646, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two years\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2659}, {\"ngram\": \"Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek senior\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2692}, {\"ngram\": \"CGTN\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At three years, snowboarding; at four years, monoskiing, then double skiing\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094so many different sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2809, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"three years\", \"from\": 2708, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"four years\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"many different sports\", \"from\": 2786, \"to\": 2807}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u008cGuided by his father's expertise, Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek won three successive youth world championships between 2016 and 2018.\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2926, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his father's expertise\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek\", \"from\": 2848, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"three successive youth world championships\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2903}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022 he became the European and World Champion \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 and in 2023, he was the world runner-up.\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 3021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2962, \"end\": 2976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"score\": 0.9999906923959556, \"rank\": 9.307628009718631e-06, \"text\": \"World Champion\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_championship\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world runner-up\", \"from\": 3001, \"to\": 3020}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek trains intensively, getting ready for the trials ahead.\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3087, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the trials\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3080}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And like all Olympians, he knows it's not merely about muscles and coordination: much of being a champion comes from winning the battle between your own ears.\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all Olympians\", \"from\": 3097, \"to\": 3110}, {\"ngram\": \"muscles\", \"from\": 3143, \"to\": 3150}, {\"ngram\": \"coordination\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"a champion\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3193}, {\"ngram\": \"the battle\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3223}, {\"ngram\": \"your own ears\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not just physical - mental battles are also hard,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3313, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"physical - mental battles\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not just a one-day, 10-minute regatta - it spans out for five days and a lot of time on the water.\\\"\", \"from\": 3314, \"to\": 3419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a one-day, 10-minute regatta\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3357}, {\"ngram\": \"five days\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3386}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3391, \"to\": 3396}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3404}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But if anyone was born for the battle, it's Vodi\\u00c5\\u00a1ek \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0093 and as a global audience watches what for many will be a brand new sport, he's hoping to be the hero of the hour.\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 3428, \"to\": 3434}, {\"ngram\": \"the battle\", \"from\": 3448, \"to\": 3458}, {\"ngram\": \"a global audience\", \"from\": 3485, \"to\": 3502}, {\"ngram\": \"a brand new sport\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3550}, {\"ngram